embed.title: Here's the commands for this bot!
embed.description: CHANGE THIS TO "Set prefix for this server: " + args[args.length-1]

fields.name: General Commands
fields.value:
help: Displays this message.
sayhelp: Displays this message, but sends it in the channel instead of DM'ing you it.
count: Shows the # of msgs that has been sent since this bot implemented this feature.
rng (num): Chooses a random number from 1 thru (num)
vote (msg): Makes a vote message.
yorn (msg): Answers a yes/no question.
send (msg): Makes me send a message. @ becomes italicized to prevent pings.
flip: Flip a coin.
rngcase (msg): Randomize the case of a message.
support: Links the support server
covid19: Provides information regarding the COVID-19 virus

fields.name: Meme Commands
fields.value:
ping: Pong.
f: Presses [F] to pay respects.
geico: Save 15% or more on car insurance.
gold: Give reddit gold.
coughcount: Shows the # of coughs (including the ones by the bot)
oof: OOF
cum: **COMSUME THE CUM CHALICE**
owoify (msg): owoifies a message

fields.name: Admin Only Commands
fields.value:
*These commands require you to have the administrator permission on your server*
prefix (prefix): Sets a new prefix for the server.
coughtimeout (num): # of coughs allowed before it times out. Is reset after a minute has passed since the first cough. Setting to a negative integer will remove it.

fields.name: No Prefix
fields.value:
ayy: lmao
owo: What's this?
Cough: Cough
me2 *or* me too *or* me to *or* me two *or* mewtwo: me too
twitch.tv/ggtylerr: two r's all lowercase
go the marcus *or* go da marcus: go da marcus
bruh: Certifies a bruh moment.
pinging me (like saying '@Bot#4200') *or* pinging me and adding help (like saying '@Bot#4200 help'): DMs you this message.

fields.name: Need help?
fields.value: Check out the support server: https://discord.gg/N5HnVrA
